  "title": "Logistics Operations Specialist",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Oversees a company's operational workflow, inventory and equipment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Resolve operational issues and disputes promptly, or prevent it from</p>\n<p>even occurring.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Maintain constant communication with managers, staff, and</p>\n<p>merchants to ensure proper operations of the company with brief</p>\n<p>summary to the Management.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Submit proposals or suggestions with supporting back up examples</p>\n<p>which can improve the workflow and increase profit margins within</p>\n<p>the organisation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Develop, implement, and maintain quality assurance protocols, this</p>\n<p>includes a proper onboarding documentation process for all</p>\n<p>departments (Operational Handbook).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>-Increase the efficiency of existing processes and procedures to</p>\n<p>enhance the company's internal capacity.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5.5 work days per week, OT when necessary.</p>\n<p>(Modays to Fridays): 9am to 6pm.</p>\n<p>(Saturdays): 9am to 1pm, excluding Sundays and Public Holidays.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Strong excel knowledge &amp; passion to go above and beyond.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Skills</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Management in Skills Multi Tasking Warehousing.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
