    "description": "<p>Simplified E-commerce Warehousing with customized requests.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Fulfilship Pte. Ltd. is a growing e-commerce fulfilment company.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our mission is to help SME grow and scale both domestically and internationally.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Overall responsible for the daily operations, including physical operations - receiving, storing, picking, packing, inventory management and worker/shift management.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Meet warehouse opertional SLA's by general management, problem-solving and employee coaching/training.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>On-site coordination with ops backend teams to ensure operational efficiency, safety and accuracy.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Analysis of the data reports to identify performance bottlenecks and improve the performance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Continuously improve the throughput and attain a sustainable level of delivery performance improvement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Workig Hours: Mondays to Fridays: 9.00 am to 6.00 pm, excluding&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Public Holidays.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Saturdays: 9.00 am to 1.00 pm.</p>\n<p># Nearest MRT Station: Joo Koon MRT.</p>\n<p># Easily Accessible: 3 Bus-Stops away from Joo Koon MRT &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Station/Bus-Interchange.</p>\n<p># 10 days Annual Leave.</p>\n<p># Condusive working environment.</p>\n<p># Team Bonus/es.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Note: We are a Yellow Ribbon Partner Employer, providing ex-&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;offenders with second chances through career &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;opportunities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
